WEBVTT

00:01.530 --> 00:03.900
I don’t want to die!

00:04.040 --> 00:05.760
I don’t want to lose my body!

00:05.760 --> 00:07.960
I want to continue living in my body.

00:08.470 --> 00:11.400
I have a tremendous fear of losing my body.

00:11.950 --> 00:16.180
Maybe you can’t understand, but that’s how a normal human being feels.

00:16.910 --> 00:20.790
Please, Lain, help me.
